{
  "stem": "16245.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, I didn't believe that anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now that came much later in the piece, that came after the Arrow Cross takeover.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the Arrow Cross took over, now that was in October 1944, you would have thought that the idiots would have known that the war was lost.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then again, look, the way they believed in the wonder weapons coming and, and beating the Allies, I mean, that, that was really, really touching in its stupidity.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's when they started to establish a ghetto in October, November 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, you've got to remember the war finished within six months.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in Budapest, they had probably three months before the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They started to build the ghetto in the vicinity where orthodox Jewry in Budapest lived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was a kind of a temporary affair with wooden, with timber walls-- but nevertheless, a ghetto, OK.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they started-- the Hungarian police started escorting Jews from the Jewish houses into the ghetto day after day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's when they set up the international ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was your original question to-- the neutral powers tried to save as many Jews as they possibly could.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now Wallenberg today is given a lot of credit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, he's given all the credit what all the neutral powers did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They did their best.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It wasn't worth a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But nevertheless, it was, it was a great help.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as luck would have it, they designated it as Swiss, into a Swiss-protected house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at the beginning, Swiss protection was OK.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And of course, it may be possible for us to stay, provided I managed to get a Swiss Schutz-pass.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I got one, a forged one, again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But nevertheless, it looked all right.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
